            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I wanted to take a moment to express my heartfelt gratitude for the incredible experience my child, Shaurya Sharma, has had at Orchids International School Wadgaonsheri. Since joining the school in class 1, and now being in class 6 A, Shaurya has flourished in ways that have exceeded our expectations.\n\nAcademically, socially, and in terms of confidence, Shaurya has grown remarkably. What we cherish most about the school is its loving and supportive environment. Every teacher goes above and beyond, genuinely caring for the students and putting their heart into their work. This dedication is evident in the way they engage with the kids daily.\n\nThe small class sizes have made a significant difference, allowing Shaurya to receive more attention, guidance, and opportunities to be heard. We also appreciate how the school values art and music, enabling Shaurya to discover new interests and take pride in their creations.\n\nThe variety of events organized by the school, such as field trips, pizza pajama parties, sports day, Republic Day, Independence Day, annual functions, and Teacher's Day celebrations, have enriched Shaurya's experience. Additionally, the school's celebration of various festivals has broadened cultural knowledge among the students.\n\nOverall, we are immensely grateful for the positive impact the school has had on Shaurya's happiness and growth. Being surrounded by people who genuinely care has made a significant difference in Shaurya's life, and it has been a perfect fit for our family.\n\nThank you once again for all that you do.",
